---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Protective Atmosphere Brazing Furnace Components" description="You need precise control over hydrogen or nitrogen atmospheres for brazed joints. Our specialized furnace accessories ensure clean, strong bonding.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Protective Atmosphere Brazing Furnace Components</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You need precise control over hydrogen or nitrogen atmospheres to ensure the integrity of your brazed joints. Our specialized furnace accessories are engineered to prevent oxidation and ensure clean, strong bonding in your protective atmosphere brazing operations. You can improve your yield rates and reduce joint failures in your heat exchangers or automotive parts by choosing our verified atmosphere control and monitoring equipment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Brazing requires ultra-low dew points and consistent gas purity. Traces of oxygen lead to weak joints and surface defects.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu offers high-precision gas flow meters and dew point monitors. You maintain the perfect environment for bonding, ensuring 100% leak-proof results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Gas Flow Meters</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Dew Point Sensors</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Ceramic Supports</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Vacuum Gaskets</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Brazing Process Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
